ZH: 乘客们正在等待飞机起飞。
EN: The passengers are waiting for the plane to take off.

ZH: 请乘客们系好安全带。
EN: Please fasten your seat belts, passengers.

ZH: 乘客可以在飞机上享用免费的饮料。
EN: Passengers can enjoy complimentary drinks on the plane.

ZH: 飞机起飞前，请关闭手机，以免干扰其他乘客。
EN: Before takeoff, please turn off your phone to avoid disturbing other passengers.

ZH: 乘客可以使用头枕来增加舒适度。
EN: Passengers can use the headrest to increase comfort.

ZH: 这辆火车的乘客满载。
EN: The passengers on this train are all full.

ZH: 火车上的乘客被要求保持安静。
EN: Passengers on the train are asked to remain quiet.

ZH: 乘客们对船上的美景赞叹不已。
EN: The passengers were amazed by the beautiful scenery on the boat.

ZH: 请尊重其他乘客的隐私。
EN: Please respect the privacy of other passengers.

ZH: 乘客们纷纷表达对服务的满意。
EN: Passengers expressed their satisfaction with the service.

ZH: 飞机上有一个不守规矩的乘客。
EN: There is a disruptive passenger on the plane.

ZH: 乘客们需要出示有效的身份证明。
EN: Passengers need to present valid identification.

ZH: 高铁上的乘客可以购买食品和饮料。
EN: Passengers on the high-speed train can purchase food and drinks.

ZH: 那位乘客拥有第一类舱的座位。
EN: That passenger has a seat in first class.

ZH: 乘客需要到指定的门口登机。
EN: Passengers need to board at the designated gate.

ZH: 有关乘客的信息会被保密。
EN: Information about passengers will be kept confidential.

ZH: 请为老人和小孩让座以便给其他乘客让出空间。
EN: Please give up your seat for the elderly and children to make space for other passengers.

ZH: 火车上有很多乘客因为车延误而感到失望。
EN: Many passengers on the train were disappointed due to the delay.

ZH: 乘客们需要准确地阅读安全指示。
EN: Passengers need to read the safety instructions carefully.

ZH: 这家航空公司提供免费的餐食供乘客享用。
EN: This airline offers complimentary meals for passengers.
